        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "在滴流床反应器中，使用一系列双功能催化剂（MoS2/Al2O3-沸石）对溶解在十二烷中的棕榈酸甲酯进行加氢转化。反应条件为：温度250–350°C，氢气压力3.0–5.0 MPa，液时空速(LHSV) 36 h−1，H2/进料比600 Nm3/m3。目标是实现含氧化合物的完全转化并通过‘直接’加氢脱氧(HDO)路径生成烷烃。",
        "text_snippet": "Hydroprocessing was performed at a temperature of 250–350◦C, hydrogen pressure of 3.0–5.0 MPa, liquid hourly space velocity (LHSV) of 36 h−1, and an H2/feed ratio of 600 Nm3/m3. Complete conversion of oxygen-containing compounds was achieved at 310◦C in the presence of MoS2/Al2O3-zeolite catalysts; the selectivity for the conversion of methyl palmitate via the ‘direct’ hydrodeoxygenation (HDO) route was over 85%.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
